/0618-16.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-17.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0529.JPG","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-1.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-2.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-3.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-4.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-5.jpg","https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-6.jpg"],"content":"<p>在全城高考的尾巴上，我和表姐出现在天河机场，假装刚刚高考完，出去浪。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0470.JPG\" width=\"3024\" height=\"3024\"></p>\n<p>第一站是山城重庆，下了飞机就下大雨，就算在本地人的带领下，也绕了半天路，晚上十二点才到住的地方。放下行李，就出门找心心念念的重庆火锅，当然点的是红油而不是鸳鸯，但就算是微辣，也不曾想当天晚上老姐就给整病了，后来就再也没碰过火锅。那天起的比较晚，还是下着雨，她拿着的，是后来遗落在稻城亚丁的透明雨伞。下午就去了磁器口逛逛，找了个小酒馆坐了坐，吃了晚饭她不舒服就回去了。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0241.JPG\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0609-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0609-2.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0609-3.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0609-4.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p>第二天她好好休息了一晚竟然就好了，下午跑到郊区去民国街玩玩，晚上自然是不能错过的洪崖洞。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0254.JPG\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0265.JPG\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0260.JPG\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-2.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-5.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-7.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-8.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-9.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-11.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-12.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0278.JPG\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-14.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-15.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p>重庆飞康定，提前给她选了个左边靠窗的座位，就是为了让她能看到蜀山之王贡嘎雪山，康定机场落地后拼车去了摄影天堂新都桥。住宿的话还是推荐住瓦泽乡，镇上附近环境好的地方不多。下午爬了下旅店后面的山，到山顶能隐约地看到远处的雪山，半山腰上有座寺庙，看守的老人很好心地给我们开门，带我们转了三圈。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0611-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0471.JPG\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p>后来也拼车去了十里长廊、塔公草原、八美，路上有薰衣草花田，回来的时候去了贡嘎雪山观景平台，上面有一大块草地，快日落的时候也拍了一段延时。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-3.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-4.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-7.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-8.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-9.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-11.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-12.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-13.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p>新都桥到稻城县香格里拉镇，途径理塘，仓央嘉措的故乡。香格里拉镇的街道很有小清新的感觉，只可惜没有时间好好逛逛。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0416.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-2.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-3.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-4.jpg\" width=\"6000\" height=\"2571\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-8.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-9.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-12.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-13.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-14.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-15.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-16.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-17.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>晚上在香格里拉镇上老姐吃到了心心念念的松茸炖鸡，她没带够衣服，只好去买了件冲锋衣，为明天爬亚丁长线做准备。</p>\n<p>稻城亚丁，从你的全世界路过里我们都心动过的地方，都向往过茅十八向荔枝求婚的场景。但现实是，去稻城亚丁，人们往往都会爬山去牛奶海和五色海，而从海拔4200米的洛绒牛场到海拔4700米的牛奶海的5km徒步过程，注定是很多人有过一次就不想再来的经历，疲惫加上缺氧导致的高原反应，会是一个很痛苦的过程，特别是对于女生来说。我们十一点到了洛绒牛场，吃了点东西就开始爬，花了三个多小时，下午两点多到的牛奶海，老姐先是吃了点抗高反的药，在开始爬舍身崖时也撑不住开始吸氧气瓶的氧气，最后一公里我推拉着她走，总算是坚持到了牛奶海，给她一点掌声。我还好没有一点反应，也没吸氧，毕竟是去过珠峰的人，从牛奶海流下来的山泉水还挺好喝，推荐有体力且没带够水的人弄一点喝。在牛奶海让一个毕业生小兄弟给我们航拍了一段，我也照例蹦哒了一下，拍了段延时，差不多三点就往下走了，六点半最后一班电瓶车。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-2.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-3.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-4.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-5.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-8.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-10.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-11.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-12.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-13.jpg\" width=\"4500\" height=\"1500\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-17.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-18.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0453.jpeg\" width=\"3024\" height=\"3024\"></p>\n<!-- <video class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://lvideo.dafork.com/FgbijuYFO7W3H9PhjD_VJuS0oOHh\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\">\n</video> -->\n<!-- <video class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://lvideo.dafork.com/FjiCi3P9BNu_usJWgpmq_oqMuYgX\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\">\n</video> -->\n<p>当天回来后，她累得不行，就已经放弃了第二天亚丁短线冲古寺到珍珠海的计划，我不能抛弃她一个人玩耍，就也没去。那天晚上到稻城县，晚上亮灯后的白塔挺好看的，当天住了一个还比较有格调的民宿，早早起了在三楼天台准备拍星空，但来之前没算好月相，当天接近满月，月亮落下去后马上就进入了蓝调时刻，想了想就拍日出算了，在天文晨始光出现后拍了段延时。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0615-1.jpg\" width=\"2250\" height=\"1500\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0615-2.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0615-5.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0615-6.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0615-7.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>稻城到色达，又路过理塘，在西城门下318此生必驾的打卡地旁拍照，就赶去色达。当晚大雨，在五明佛学院的山顶等天黑灯亮。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0616-2.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0616-3.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0616-4.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0616-5.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0616-6.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>白天天晴的佛学院好看，她披上准备好的红色围巾，走到坛城转了三圈佛塔，许了个愿。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-2.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-4.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-5.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-6.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-8.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-9.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-10.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-11.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-12.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-13.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>中午的时候赶去看天葬，一大群秃鹫在山坡上早就饥渴难耐，等到天葬师一走就一拥而上。晚上到毕棚沟住，当天晚上十点四百公里外的宜宾发生了六级地震，我们没什么感觉。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-14.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-15.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>毕棚沟经汶川回成都，去了两个藏寨，回映秀司机老家，看了下地震后恢复的模样。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-7.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-8.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-9.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0512.JPG\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-10.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-11.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-12.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-13.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-14.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-15.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-16.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-17.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0529.JPG\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>回到成都后，累得不想动，没有去锦里宽窄，就在附近找了个园区逛逛，和老姐聊聊人生，给她最后拍一点糖水片。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-1.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-2.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-3.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-4.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-5.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-6.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>故事的最后，有一段三千多张照片拼成的两分多钟延时视频。记得16年我和某人看完从你的全世界路过，从电影院出来后，她问过我一个问题，说幺鸡为什么直到一年后才去找陈末，我说她想让自己变得更好，更好的人才会遇见更好的幸福，同时时间也会留下对的人。要是现在，我会用一句赫本的话说，我当然不会试图摘月，我要月亮奔我而来。</p>\n<!-- <video class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://lvideo.dafork.com/ll86BRJ25Dh-uX2zuYxBtw-mUKpm\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\">\n</video> -->\n<div style=\"padding-top: 56.25%;position: relative;\"><iframe src=\"//player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=BV1t5411j7DB&page=1&high_quality=1&danmaku=0\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"position: absolute;height: 100%;width: 100%;top: 0;left: 0;\"></iframe></div>\n\n<audio src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=432509483.mp3\" poster=\"http://p1.music.126.net/zGgUaGvXapKMy5tfQIB7cw==/109951163167743834.jpg?param=130y130\" name=\"全世界谁倾听你\" author=\"林宥嘉\" loop autoplay><br></audio>","more":"<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0470.JPG\" width=\"3024\" height=\"3024\"></p>\n<p>第一站是山城重庆，下了飞机就下大雨，就算在本地人的带领下，也绕了半天路，晚上十二点才到住的地方。放下行李，就出门找心心念念的重庆火锅，当然点的是红油而不是鸳鸯，但就算是微辣，也不曾想当天晚上老姐就给整病了，后来就再也没碰过火锅。那天起的比较晚，还是下着雨，她拿着的，是后来遗落在稻城亚丁的透明雨伞。下午就去了磁器口逛逛，找了个小酒馆坐了坐，吃了晚饭她不舒服就回去了。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0241.JPG\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0609-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0609-2.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0609-3.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0609-4.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p>第二天她好好休息了一晚竟然就好了，下午跑到郊区去民国街玩玩，晚上自然是不能错过的洪崖洞。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0254.JPG\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0265.JPG\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0260.JPG\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-2.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-5.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-7.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-8.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-9.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-11.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-12.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0278.JPG\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-14.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0610-15.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p>重庆飞康定，提前给她选了个左边靠窗的座位，就是为了让她能看到蜀山之王贡嘎雪山，康定机场落地后拼车去了摄影天堂新都桥。住宿的话还是推荐住瓦泽乡，镇上附近环境好的地方不多。下午爬了下旅店后面的山，到山顶能隐约地看到远处的雪山，半山腰上有座寺庙，看守的老人很好心地给我们开门，带我们转了三圈。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0611-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0471.JPG\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p>后来也拼车去了十里长廊、塔公草原、八美，路上有薰衣草花田，回来的时候去了贡嘎雪山观景平台，上面有一大块草地，快日落的时候也拍了一段延时。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-3.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-4.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-7.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-8.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-9.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-11.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-12.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0612-13.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p>新都桥到稻城县香格里拉镇，途径理塘，仓央嘉措的故乡。香格里拉镇的街道很有小清新的感觉，只可惜没有时间好好逛逛。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0416.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-2.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-3.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-4.jpg\" width=\"6000\" height=\"2571\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-8.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-9.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-12.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-13.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-14.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-15.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-16.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0613-17.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>晚上在香格里拉镇上老姐吃到了心心念念的松茸炖鸡，她没带够衣服，只好去买了件冲锋衣，为明天爬亚丁长线做准备。</p>\n<p>稻城亚丁，从你的全世界路过里我们都心动过的地方，都向往过茅十八向荔枝求婚的场景。但现实是，去稻城亚丁，人们往往都会爬山去牛奶海和五色海，而从海拔4200米的洛绒牛场到海拔4700米的牛奶海的5km徒步过程，注定是很多人有过一次就不想再来的经历，疲惫加上缺氧导致的高原反应，会是一个很痛苦的过程，特别是对于女生来说。我们十一点到了洛绒牛场，吃了点东西就开始爬，花了三个多小时，下午两点多到的牛奶海，老姐先是吃了点抗高反的药，在开始爬舍身崖时也撑不住开始吸氧气瓶的氧气，最后一公里我推拉着她走，总算是坚持到了牛奶海，给她一点掌声。我还好没有一点反应，也没吸氧，毕竟是去过珠峰的人，从牛奶海流下来的山泉水还挺好喝，推荐有体力且没带够水的人弄一点喝。在牛奶海让一个毕业生小兄弟给我们航拍了一段，我也照例蹦哒了一下，拍了段延时，差不多三点就往下走了，六点半最后一班电瓶车。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-2.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-3.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-4.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-5.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-8.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-10.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-11.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-12.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-13.jpg\" width=\"4500\" height=\"1500\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-17.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0614-18.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0453.jpeg\" width=\"3024\" height=\"3024\"></p>\n<!-- <video class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://lvideo.dafork.com/FgbijuYFO7W3H9PhjD_VJuS0oOHh\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\">\n</video> -->\n<!-- <video class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://lvideo.dafork.com/FjiCi3P9BNu_usJWgpmq_oqMuYgX\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\">\n</video> -->\n<p>当天回来后，她累得不行，就已经放弃了第二天亚丁短线冲古寺到珍珠海的计划，我不能抛弃她一个人玩耍，就也没去。那天晚上到稻城县，晚上亮灯后的白塔挺好看的，当天住了一个还比较有格调的民宿，早早起了在三楼天台准备拍星空，但来之前没算好月相，当天接近满月，月亮落下去后马上就进入了蓝调时刻，想了想就拍日出算了，在天文晨始光出现后拍了段延时。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0615-1.jpg\" width=\"2250\" height=\"1500\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0615-2.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0615-5.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0615-6.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0615-7.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>稻城到色达，又路过理塘，在西城门下318此生必驾的打卡地旁拍照，就赶去色达。当晚大雨，在五明佛学院的山顶等天黑灯亮。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0616-2.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0616-3.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0616-4.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0616-5.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0616-6.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>白天天晴的佛学院好看，她披上准备好的红色围巾，走到坛城转了三圈佛塔，许了个愿。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-1.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-2.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-4.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-5.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-6.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-8.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-9.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-10.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-11.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-12.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-13.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>中午的时候赶去看天葬，一大群秃鹫在山坡上早就饥渴难耐，等到天葬师一走就一拥而上。晚上到毕棚沟住，当天晚上十点四百公里外的宜宾发生了六级地震，我们没什么感觉。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-14.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0617-15.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>毕棚沟经汶川回成都，去了两个藏寨，回映秀司机老家，看了下地震后恢复的模样。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-7.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-8.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-9.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0512.JPG\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-10.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-11.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-12.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-13.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-14.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-15.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-16.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-17.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/IMG_0529.JPG\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>回到成都后，累得不想动，没有去锦里宽窄，就在附近找了个园区逛逛，和老姐聊聊人生，给她最后拍一点糖水片。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-1.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-2.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-3.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-4.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-5.jpg\" width=\"2000\" height=\"3000\"></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium\" src=\"https://jsd.cdn.zzko.cn/gh/zhinieing/picx-images-hosting@master/chuanxi/0618-6.jpg\" width=\"3000\" height=\"2000\"></p>\n<p>故事的最后，有一段三千多张照片拼成的两分多钟延时视频。记得16年我和某人看完从你的全世界路过，从电影院出来后，她问过我一个问题，说幺鸡为什么直到一年后才去找陈末，我说她想让自己变得更好，更好的人才会遇见更好的幸福，同时时间也会留下对的人。要是现在，我会用一句赫本的话说，我当然不会试图摘月，我要月亮奔我而来。</p>\n<!-- <video class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://lvideo.dafork.com/ll86BRJ25Dh-uX2zuYxBtw-mUKpm\" preload=\"metadata\" controls=\"controls\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\">\n</video> -->\n<div style=\"padding-top: 56.25%;position: relative;\"><iframe src=\"//player.bilibili.com/player.html?bvid=BV1t5411j7DB&page=1&high_quality=1&danmaku=0\" scrolling=\"no\" border=\"0\" frameborder=\"no\" framespacing=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"position: absolute;height: 100%;width: 100%;top: 0;left: 0;\"></iframe></div>\n\n<audio src=\"http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=432509483.mp3\" poster=\"http://p1.music.126.net/zGgUaGvXapKMy5tfQIB7cw==/109951163167743834.jpg?param=130y130\" name=\"全世界谁倾听你\" author=\"林宥嘉\" loop autoplay><br></audio>","categories":[{"name":"travel","path":"api/categories/travel.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"重庆","path":"api/tags/重庆.json"},{"name":"稻城亚丁","path":"api/tags/稻城亚丁.json"},{"name":"色达","path":"api/tags/色达.json"},{"name":"川西","path":"api/tags/川西.json"},{"name":"成都","path":"api/tags/成都.json"},{"name":"topic","path":"api/tags/topic.json"}]}